-- RWE Workers to Walk Out at Power Plants in Germany Tomorrow, Union Says
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-12-15T11:04:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-15/rwe-workers-to-walk-out-at-power-plants-in-germany-tomorrow-union-says.html
Some 16,000 RWE AG workers will
strike three hours daily on Thursday and Friday, the IG BCE
labor union said in an statement on its website today. The
walkouts will include power plants, the union said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
